function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	local pos01 = Hydra.ActorGetPosition(Marker_Location_01)
	local pos02 = Hydra.ActorGetPosition(Marker_Location_02)
	
	-- Set Ancillary Fallen AI enabled, run back to position
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(Fallen_04) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(Fallen_04)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToPositionConstantSpeed(Fallen_04, pos02, Hydra.MOVE_RATE_SPRINT, 1.0)
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(Fallen_06) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(Fallen_06)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToPositionConstantSpeed(Fallen_06, pos01, Hydra.MOVE_RATE_SPRINT, 1.0)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
-- Set Team for Barrel trap
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(Barrel) then
		Hydra.ActorSetTeam(Barrel, Hydra.TEAM_PLAYER_DEFAULT)
	end
	
	-- Set Primary Fallen AI enabled
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(Fallen_01) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(Fallen_01)
		Hydra.ActorAIForcePrimaryTarget(Fallen_01,Barrel)
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(Fallen_02) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(Fallen_02)
		Hydra.ActorAIForcePrimaryTarget(Fallen_02,Barrel)
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(Fallen_03) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(Fallen_03)
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(Fallen_05) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(Fallen_05)
	end
end

function Start(idActorDamager, idActorDamaged)

	local player1 = Hydra.ActorGetPlayersAndPetsInRange(Marker_Location_01, 30, false,false)[1]
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(Fallen_01) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(player1) then
		-- Grunt taunt audio 
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(Fallen_01, "fallen_grunt_taunt")
		-- Set New Target
		Hydra.ActorAIForcePrimaryTarget(Fallen_01,player1)
		
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(Fallen_02) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(player1)  then
		-- Set New Target
		Hydra.ActorAIForcePrimaryTarget(Fallen_02,player1)
	end		
	
	Hydra.EventSend("DOV_Barrel_Gameplay_Moment")
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	-- Set Primary Fallen AI enabled
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(Fallen_01) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(Fallen_01)
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(Fallen_02) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(Fallen_02)
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(Fallen_03) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(Fallen_03)
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(Fallen_05) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(Fallen_05)
	end
end
